The Ford Fusion is a mid-sized sedan and thus competes in an incredibly competitive segment, going up against other heavyweights in its class and Ford has priced the car accordingly, with models starting at $22,000. With the largest selection of cars from dealers and private sellers, Autotrader can help find the perfect Fusion for you.
